      "title": "Reduced power outage time",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission has given permission to implement a 1-hour power cut from tomorrow (06) to Friday (09) as requested by the Sri Lanka Electricity Board.",
        "Accordingly, 1 hour power cut will be enforced in 20 zones from A to W from tomorrow (06) to 9th from 6 pm to 9 pm."
      ],
